## Welcome to the future of streaming lossless compression.

Experience deplump general purpose lossless compression right now (2Mb limit):  
______________________
To *deplump* (compress) a file use:

<form action="DeplumpServlet" enctype="multipart/form-data" method="post">
<input type="file" name="datafile" size="40"></input>
<input type="submit" value="Deplump"></input>
</form>

<p></p>
To *plump* (decompress) a previously deplumped file use:
<form action="PlumpServlet" enctype="multipart/form-data" method="post">
<input type="file" name="datafile" size="40"></input>
<input type="submit" value="Plump"></input>
</form>

